channel.title: Washington DC area #2 (Gina)
channel.description: Code Monkey visits Greenbelt, MD, Busch Gardens, VA, and Washington, DC. Please see my very extended version at: http://tinyurl.com/5eannr

item.title: P1010099.JPG
item.description: Code Monkey gets to Greenbelt and meets a little cousin of his. JoCo Monkey has a JoCo tattoo on his chest, drawn by JoCo himself.
